  body
    header
      #navbarHeader.bg-dark.collapse(style='')
        .container
          .row
            .col-sm-8.col-md-7.py-4
              h4.text-white About
              p.text-muted
                | I wanted to make resource gathering easier by having a place where I could store relevant resource and find them easily. So I decided to create Bookshelff.
            .col-sm-4.col-md-3.py-4
              h4.text-white Contact
              span.list-unstyled
                
                a.text-white.contact-font(href='#')
                  span.spacing.hi-icon.fa-stack.fa-lg(style='font-size: .5rem;')
                    i.fa.fa-linkedin.fa-stack-2x
                   
                a.text-white.contact-font(href='#')
                  span.spacing.hi-icon.fa-stack.fa-lg(style='font-size: .5rem;')
                    i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-stack-2x
                   
                 
                 
              

      .navbar.navbar-dark.bg-dark.box-shadow
        .container.d-flex.justify-content-between
          a.navbar-brand.d-flex.align-items-center(href='/')
            strong Home
          button.navbar-toggler.collapsed(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarHeader', aria-controls='navbarHeader', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
            span.navbar-toggler-icon
